{
  "stem": "22869.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "All of a sudden, had-- we had no problems of having warm clothing, because they did not watch us, the SS, the [INAUDIBLE] We still had to have our uniform, but under the uniform we could wear just almost anything you wanted to.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I was working in this place there under this guy's guidance, so to say, until one day he got angry at me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I don't recall for what.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he came, and he slapped me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So here, I tell myself, here is somebody who's supposed to be my buddy, my-- my-- my guy who's supposed to help me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He slapped me for some little thing that I did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I don't remember what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So I was very, like, hurt personally that I followed him in order to have it a little better.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And now he himself is beating me up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He's a kapo.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He had all the right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I mean, nobody denied him that right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So I was trying to get out of this job that I was doing right now.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I was looking into different things that I could do there to get out from under his hands, because I was like, kind of insulted, if you can understand that.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one day, they were telling us that they were looking for a man who's in charge in the camp-- in this particular camp-- of the food.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Meaning, not the food that is brought in with the packages, but every camp had a detail-- that used to go to the main camp to draw your daily rations.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like I mentioned, the coffee, the bread, the margarine, steaks, or whatever they gave you.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
